ransplanting, Top dressing at 20, 40, 60 days after transplanting (DAT)\", \"organic_alternatives\": \"FYM 25 t/ha, Vermicompost 10 t/ha\", \"recommended_fertilizer\": \"DAP + Urea\"}','{\"harvest_method\": \"Manual hand-picking\", \"harvest_duration\": \"120-140 DAT\", \"best_harvest_time\": \"Early morning when the soil is moist and the sun is not intense to prevent damage to the bulbs\", \"equipment_required\": [\"Gloves\", \"Twine or string for tying the onions\", \"Sharp knife or pruning shears\"], \"harvest_indicators\": [\"Fruit color change from green to yellow or red\", \"Firmness test: Onion should be firm to the touch\", \"Leaf senescence: Leaves turn yellow and wilt\", \"Neck diameter: 1-2 cm\"], \"post_harvest_losses\": \"Typical post-harvest loss percentage: 5-10%, can be reduced by proper curing and storage\", \"pre_harvest_interval\": \"At least 14 days after pesticide application\", \"yield_considerations\": \"Expected yield per hectare: 25-30 tons under good conditions and 15-20 tons under poor conditions\", \"expected_harvest_date\": \"October-November\"}','{\"current\": {\"rain_mm\": 0.1, \"condition\": \"Thunderstorm\", \"feels_like_c\": 38.6, \"temperature_c\": 36.1, \"wind_speed_kmh\": 9.9, \"humidity_percent\": 40, \"precipitation_mm\": 0.1, \"wind_direction_deg\": 279, \"cloud_cover_percent\": 9}, \"latitude\": 28.6139, \"timezone\": \"Asia/Kolkata\", \"longitude\": 77.209, \"fetched_at\": \"2026-06-15T10:08:38.946718Z\", \"forecast_7_days\": [{\"date\": \"2026-06-15\", \"condition\": \"Thunderstorm\", \"temp_max_c\": 37.0, \"temp_min_c\": 27.5, \"wind_speed_kmh\": 11.9, \"precipitation_mm\": 0.7}, {\"date\": \"2026-06-16\", \"condition\": \"Thunderstorm\", \"temp_max_c\": 38.9, \"temp_min_c\": 26.0, \"wind_speed_kmh\": 11.5, \"precipitation_mm\": 0.4}, {\"date\": \"2026-06-17\", \"condition\": \"Thunderstorm\", \"temp_max_c\": 40.2, \"temp_min_c\": 29.4, \"wind_speed_kmh\": 12.1, \"precipitation_mm\": 0.0}, {\"date\": \"2026-06-18\", \"cond